],"class_list":["post-28710","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-sin-al-ithm","tag-abuse-al-sibab","tag-backbiting-gheeba","tag-bad-deeds-al-sayyiat","tag-curses-al-laan","tag-gossip-al-namimah","tag-guarding-the-tongue","tag-insults-al-shatm","tag-major-sins-al-kabair","tag-manners-adab","tag-reciprocity-al-tabadul","tag-reputation-al-ird","tag-slander-al-buhtan","tag-wrongdoing-al-thulm"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-7t4","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":7501,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/curse-own-parents\/","url_meta":{"origin":28710,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Curses: Prohibition of cursing another&#8217;s parents","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, among the major sins is that a man curses his own parents.\u201d It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how can a man curse his own parents?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHe insults the father\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/sahaba-viewed-cursing-kabair\/","url_meta":{"origin":28710,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Curses: We viewed cursing brothers as major sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Yazid ibn Abi \u2018Ubayd reported: Salamah ibn al-Akwa\u2019, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf we saw a man curse his brother, we considered it as if he had come to a door of mortal sin.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 6674 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u064a\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u062f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32841,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/21\/three-worst-major-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":28710,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Kaba\u2019ir: Three of the worst major sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said three times, \u201cShall I not tell you about the worst of major sins?\u201d They said, \u201cOf course, O Messenger of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThey are to associate partners with Allah and to be disrespectful to parents.\u201d Then,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42172,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/08\/23\/if-avoid-kabair\/","url_meta":{"origin":28710,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Paradise if believers avoid major sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever comes worshiping Allah without associating anything with Him, performing the prayer, giving the charity, and avoiding the major sins, he will have Paradise.\u201d They asked him about the major sins, and the Prophet said, \u201cIdolatry\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20436,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/05\/intercession-major-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":28710,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sins: We have hope for people of major sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: We withheld ourselves from seeking forgiveness for people of major sins until we heard our Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, say, \u201cVerily, I have delayed my intercession for the people of major sins among my nation for the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Ibn Umar said, \"Thus,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42699,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/07\/despair-major-sin\/","url_meta":{"origin":28710,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Kaba\u2019ir: Despairing of Allah\u2019s mercy a major sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 7, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are the major sins?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him said, \u201cIdolatry with Allah, losing hope in relief from Allah, and despair in the mercy of Allah.\u201d Source: Kashf al-Asta\u0304r 106 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonlin